{"tid":151723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實由幾時開始，香港啲中學生係講普通話，而唔係廣東話？","createTime":"2017-03-11T06:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-11T11:32:13.000Z","uid":35425,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"83feee5c565894345956b41bbffba2f1aedb7454","tid":151723,"uid":35425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:39:16.000Z","msg":"其實由幾時開始，香港啲中學生係講普通話，而唔係廣東話？到底係我少出街，定係個世界已經變得太快，快到我跟唔到？<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始，原來揹書包係一種罪過，因為會阻住周圍嘅人？但拖行李果啲又無問題，並唔係話令兩者對立。但當被行李阻住嘅人都未出聲嘅時候，反而仲要比人批鬥？<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始，香港嘅樓已經唔再係比香港人住。香港大學畢業生講緊平均起薪係12k嘅時候，然後講緊南昌站新起嘅單位賣緊萬九蚊呎，仲有打哂蛇餅有幾百人睇個得300幾呎嘅示範單位，係咪真係新果一代實在太唔捱得，追唔到時代嘅節奏？<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始，差唔多每個月都有學生自殺？死左之後，教育局長仲要出黎話唔關佢事，要趕住去旅行云云，某啲人仲話係啲學生唔捱得，太悲觀。就連我地成年人都對自己嘅未來無希望嘅時候，你叫啲細路點對自己有希望，對未來抱有希望？<br />\n<br />\n由幾時開始，警察打人會係正確？被法庭判有罪之後，某政黨竟然可以擺街站，叫人簽名支持七警，仲呼籲大家捐錢。大佬呀，依家犯左法呀，無論係咩身份，打人犯法被判有罪，好理所當然啫，下麻？<br />\n<br />\n我都唔知由幾時開始，好多好荒謬嘅事，今日都變成事實。<br />\n<br />\n近排成日諗起呢句說話：<br />\n以前我地住嘅地方叫香港<br />\n今日我地住喺一個叫香港嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多好多好多....到底有邊個可以話比我知，呢啲野到底係幾時開始？"},{"pid":"2afea84128563f2c59fd7e53897743fb60f9da52","tid":151723,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:39:58.000Z","msg":"幾時開始？不嬲都進行緊"},{"pid":"fcdf63bf1bfb2ec90cb1cf05a91be4fc4b1c5310","tid":151723,"uid":54593,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:45:25.000Z","msg":"呢啲文章多到開始睇到厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18de432d37cae01af38ebe36ce2fb1a645498087","tid":151723,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T06:45:42.000Z","msg":"講蝗話嗰啲都係新移民嚟"},{"pid":"f9bea7b2bdebf00c1a3dac58326715460d228f0d","tid":151723,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"由每日一百五十人加速ing"},{"pid":"94dbf817d99e1d7cc7da37b874805d59550e883b","tid":151723,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:25:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由每日一百五十人加速ing</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點止呀，七年專材呢？投資移民呢？<br />\n<br />\n尤其係七年人士，從來無公佈每年有幾多人，多過每日百五都未定"},{"pid":"8c7c9394baac57394124296671f4d2d97d70b02f","tid":151723,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6785fde94e8b8c352ceaefa95e69ba589d9aef5d","tid":151723,"uid":34147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:47:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢啲文章多到開始睇到厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個個都嚟發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 正如個陣雨傘後成立嘅新組織，個個都係「經歷雨傘運動後.... 香港正值風雨飄遙... 我哋企出嚟....」"},{"pid":"d97b3e56e567db882d0a0010d7295687e5c695ba","tid":151723,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"90年代出世既已經係最後一代香港人"},{"pid":"506a4aaf45e9926d69a0089f3e47b734d2141e36","tid":151723,"uid":45252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:53:16.000Z","msg":"好撚煩呀白痴仔<br />\n你之前去左火星呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵鬼唔知"},{"pid":"453cc543ea2f183638e72fcc7730f36199a0f77f","tid":151723,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:56:08.000Z","msg":"好快 香港人就會被取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d079cca18507c838176a5d170af608581c30b943","tid":151723,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T07:57:21.000Z","msg":"蝗族絕對需要清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8003c80003e615e6024fd9e9ac20ffbdc381ba","tid":151723,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:16:15.000Z","msg":"689上任後就加劇了！"},{"pid":"f4ab14b369e7963112d90e30ac536e08ebbfc53b","tid":151723,"uid":48358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:19:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>90年代出世既已經係最後一代香港人</blockquote><br />\n呢個真"},{"pid":"1e49ede09efedbea91b4e20d20e7dac27b8d3494","tid":151723,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>90年代出世既已經係最後一代香港人</blockquote><br />\n呢個真</blockquote><br />\n有幸成為90後<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5fe27b4db5de4bc46680c11e045f442b7643a07","tid":151723,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:26:15.000Z","msg":"廣東話係低賤語言，搵唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d80743f822f40a95808f2445d0fc028823627c86","tid":151723,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:53:32.000Z","msg":"因為Hong Kong已經成為Xianggang"},{"pid":"fbb18f68bf7d0acf11925abddd0d168d77c1e65b","tid":151723,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:54:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>廣東話係低賤語言，搵唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知由幾時開始香港人開始貶低屬於自己本身既野<br />\n搵唔倒錢既野就覺得係低賤 證明你成家都好低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7750954b5baa69e92add5cc55ceb2a8c228d1ec2","tid":151723,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:59:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廣東話係低賤語言，搵唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知由幾時開始香港人開始貶低屬於自己本身既野<br />\n搵唔倒錢既野就覺得係低賤 證明你成家都好低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開埠至今，廣東話從來都係地底泥！以前俾英文踐踏，而家多埋普通話。香港的社會上層及精英，冇任何人以廣東話為榮！事實就係事實！！"},{"pid":"73f459ba1ef6d3ba7f589d9176a355d399d15410","tid":151723,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:41:35.000Z","msg":"認真邊一個區依家係最嚴重<br />\n利申天水圍，情況仲係可以控制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6080004071dd468106783eaa119887fe6a229a6","tid":151723,"uid":6195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:54:50.000Z","msg":"幾時開始 市面出現大量垃圾 <br />\n廢老 廢中 大陸人 師奶 蝗蟲 蝗卵<br />\n<br />\n搭車 -<br />\n唔係打尖插隊 就呃兩蚊八達通 專企樓梯位 屙屎剪指甲食嘢開喇叭咩都有。<br />\n<br />\n搭地鐵 - <br />\n專搵繁忙時間先出街 仲要妹下妹下慢慢行。啲阿毛就個撚個去到閘口先慢慢拎個袋出黎磨吓磨吓。<br />\n<br />\n買野食 - <br />\n去撚到counter先慢慢諗食咩⋯⋯又改三改四。食野食撚到喂狗咁。<br />\n<br />\n櫃員機 - <br />\n襟一個制又要諗一分鐘。拎完錢又再入過張卡。再黎。<br />\n<br />\n數之不盡.....<br />\n<br />\n嚴重影響都市節奏。"},{"pid":"8a3a44e354e348a6ac638c3d7d78f019c74ce229","tid":151723,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T10:56:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>廣東話係低賤語言，搵唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知由幾時開始香港人開始貶低屬於自己本身既野<br />\n搵唔倒錢既野就覺得係低賤 證明你成家都好低賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人都係閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做服務業就知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe219285587bf9f55893cfede1f01b10b3208dec","tid":151723,"uid":62318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:01:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca310bb39bfaa94b3d63557ea8838a4f4a4eaeaf","tid":151723,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:05:44.000Z","msg":"當..."},{"pid":"14c40c38a89cc8ee0d7b06bb67b91b2ec3255026","tid":151723,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T11:25:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當...</blockquote><br />\n當一...."}]}